.row
  .span4.offset1
    %h1 Sign up your group
    %p 30 day free trial
    %h6 No credit card required
    = render 'sign_up_form'

  .span4
    .info-box#organisation
      %h2 $5/person/month
      %p For this amazing price you get lots of reassuring things like:
      %ul
        %li Privacy
        %li A banner for your mug
        %li Printable discussions
        %li And a whole lot more...
      %br
      %p At the end of 30 days, we'll ask you to enter a credit card to continue to use Loomio. We'll send you a reminder to let you know.
      %p
        If this does not sound like it suits your group
        = link_to 'see Pay What You Can', '/group_requests/3/group_sign_up_informal'
